40:### Fixed
41:
42:- **`setMeta` rejects non-finite numbers** (`NaN`, `Infinity`, `-Infinity`). Previously these were accepted and silently coerced to `null` by `JSON.stringify`, causing in-memory state to diverge from the persisted snapshot. (M_NEW2)
