17:- **Regression tests:**
18:  - `World.deserialize` rejects malformed snapshots whose `tags` or `metadata` reference dead entities (locks in L_NEW4).
19:  - Legacy v0.4.x snapshot fields (`config.detectInPlacePositionMutations`, `componentOptions[*].detectInPlaceMutations`) are silently ignored on read (locks in the v0.5.0 backward-compat promise).
