I found one concrete thing worth digging on before I decide sign-off: the architecture doc still appears to describe removed v0.5.0 behavior in a few places, despite the v0.5.4 “doc drift fixed” claim. I’m doing a narrow repo-wide search now for those removed symbols/semantics to see whether this is isolated wording or a broader remaining inconsistency.
