`maxTicksPerFrame`, `instrumentationProfile`, and per-component `ComponentStoreOptions` (diffMode + 
detectInPlaceMutations). v4 snapshots stay readable. |
docs\architecture\drift-log.md:30:| 2026-04-25 | ComponentStore.detectInPlaceMutations option | Lets callers opt out 
